nodes.text: Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2017 is the annual special issue of Star Wars Insider, which was released on November 15, 2016. It includes interviews and in-depth features.

The eighth volume of Star Wars Insider's yearly collections of material includes classic features including interviews with actor John Boyega (Finn in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens) and writer Lawrence Kasdan (Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens) alongside all-new material exclusive to this collection!
